The paper also involves the use of path integral representation and sampling methods, which are commonly used in control theory and system identification, suggesting cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the second likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques to alleviate the issue of local optima, suggesting cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the third likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of numerical optimization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and computer vision, suggesting cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the fourth and fifth likely sub-categories, respectively.
